{"tid":1395190,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想打去加拿大中文電台講香港情況，可否幫幫我度下點講","createTime":"2019-08-01T16:19:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T07:04:50.000Z","uid":281837,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a1e181c6bde95223d3b978d8c3ed8d163cf4154e","tid":1395190,"uid":281837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:19:26.000Z","msg":"首先，我有朋友已搬左過加拿大住一段日子，佢發覺加拿大港人移民以淺藍絲為主，本身對香港情況唔太貼地。佢地認為在香港搞好經濟民生就ok，唔好搞咁多事。<br />\n<br />\n最仆街嘅係，果度嘅香港移民以前係為左避共產黨先走，但去到又擁護返共匪。另一方面，當地華人電視電台節目都以親共言論居多(可能俾人收編左)，所以我有D想試打去佢地phone in 節目度，以香港人角度講講香港情況。<br />\n<br />\n小弟已非後生仔，雖仲有一顆熱辣辣嘅心但對口才實冇太大信心，所以為左精簡，想係度求求各巴打絲打，幫幫我整理下打到入去時講D咩最好。目標係令到佢地知道香港人想同佢地講咩。<br />\n<br />\ninfo: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am1470.com/program_pop_detail.php?type=am&amp;id=12\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am1470.com%2Fprogram_pop_detail.php%3Ftype%3Dam%26id%3D12&d=oOhF4K9gmG%2F73F8T9h6VFMtNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=d0658dc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am1470.com/program_pop_detail.php?type=am&amp;id=12</a><br />\n<br />\n時間:<br />\n溫哥華 (PDT): Mon-Fri 5pm-6pm <br />\n香港時間: 8am - 9am"},{"pid":"ffe100d8620a9136a5548c685beb9d96471e5f71","tid":1395190,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:25:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d670cda8ae81bb91620aeb22fda99b83a5bad0db","tid":1395190,"uid":281837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:26:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb7d65dd0ceaa9605b2ca3b4fffa05a79ee9c06a","tid":1395190,"uid":220316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:04:50.000Z","msg":"個電台同電視係深藍㗎，幫香港政苦同差佬㗎，10個聽眾打上去，9.5個都話遊行搞亂香港同埋係暴徒，我老豆話電台啲人係filter過啲打上去嘅聽眾㗎"}]}